    General Stores in Vikhroli, Mumbai

    General Stores in Vikhroli, Mumbai

    In India, general stores or mom-n-pop shops are generally referred to as 'kiranas'. It is a form of traditional retail where it offers a wide range of products. Now with the emergence of the various forms of modern retail, many of these establishments are evolving from its traditional format to a more modern, department store format. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. A modern general store may have air-conditioning, a wider range of products and services that local shops may not offer. Following the traditional system, most serve customers through a counter system, certain stores encourage self-service for their customers, by following a more modern system. Aiming for the convenience of the locals, these general stores also offer complimentary doorstep delivery services. You can find one from a large number of General Stores in Vikhroli, Mumbai from the list given above.
